metadata.description:
# Gooseship

Recently, there was a pleasing development in the NFT world and Dmitri Cherniak's work was sold for 6.2M.
While following the developments in the NFT world, as a 3D artist, I usually work on 3D versions of popular works.

When I first looked at this work, various objects came to my mind. Finally, I saw it closer to a spaceship and created Goosehip.

Only 1 edition was minted. 
This auction is only available those who have 
- [InfiNifty card 2023](https://www.niftygateway.com/itemdetail/primary/0xede6b3aa3a5b559fedaacc9a0b6da8ea65027271/1) and
- [Spiral](https://www.niftygateway.com/itemdetail/primary/0x0ceed9e892b15301c3f9f07d11846774f0b84844/1)
works will be able to participate.
